snippet.title: Cubism - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Try the free demo: 
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/804530/Cubism/
Itch.io - https://thomasvanbouwel.itch.io/cubism

Cubism is a simple yet challenging VR puzzlegame.
Inspired by classic solid dissection puzzles like the Soma cube, players have to assemble increasingly complex shapes out of smaller puzzle pieces. 

website http://www.cubism-vr.com/
twitter https://twitter.com/cubismvr?lang=en
facebook https://twitter.com/cubismvr?lang=en

This trailer was first debuted at the 2017 BitAwards in New York.
https://www.thebitawards.com/

Song: Gymnopédie No.1 (Lent et douloureux) - Erik Satie
Recorded by Gabriela Estácio https://soundcloud.com/gabrielaestacio
